structure.unit: B HOUSING, BUILDINGS, AND CONSTRUCTION - BUILDING CODE

law.text: Failure to comply with any order under KRS 198B.625 or the violation of KRS 198B.550 to 198B.630 or any regulation issued thereunder shall constitute a Class B misdemeanor.
law.history: Created 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 383, sec. 18, effective July 13, 1984.
